<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Html on Today I Learned</title><link>https://skalt.github.io/til/tags/html/</link><description>Recent content in Html on Today I Learned</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</copyright><atom:link href="https://skalt.github.io/til/tags/html/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title/><link>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/01/10/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/01/10/</guid><description>&lt;p>Of the &lt;a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/caption">html table &lt;code>&amp;lt;caption&amp;gt;&lt;/code> element&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/09/20/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/09/20/</guid><description>&lt;p>A hack to detect if an element is visible/not:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-js" data-lang="js">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kr">const&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">isVisible&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">el&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">=&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">el&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">offsetWidth&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">||&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">el&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">offsetHeight&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mi">0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>see &lt;a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1343237/how-to-check-elements-visibility-via-javascript">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1343237/how-to-check-elements-visibility-via-javascript&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/12/18/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/12/18/</guid><description>&lt;p>That you can group fields in an html form with a &lt;code>&amp;lt;fieldset&amp;gt;&lt;/code> tag, and that it accepts a top-level child &lt;code>&amp;lt;legend&amp;gt;&lt;/code> tag. Together,&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">fieldset&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">legend&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>Legend&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">legend&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>...&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">div&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">&amp;lt;/&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">fieldset&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>produces&lt;/p>
&lt;pre tabindex="0">&lt;code> ┌────legend─────┐
│ │
│ │
│ ... │
│ │
│ │
└───────────────┘
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;p>which is simultaneously cool and hard to style.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title/><link>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/12/26/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://skalt.github.io/til/2022/12/26/</guid><description>&lt;p>That you need to set a &lt;code>value=&amp;quot;number&amp;quot;&lt;/code> attribute AND a &lt;code>max=&amp;quot;number&amp;quot;&lt;/code> attribute on a html &lt;code>&amp;lt;progress&amp;gt;&lt;/code> element in order to display fractional progress.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>See &lt;a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>